{
  "stem": "1173.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father had only a sister and one brother, but I had many cousins, and, and I'm sorry to say that only my two uncles who left for Israel-- to Palestine, and their families survive.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All others did not survive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I do remember at my grandfather's house, which was on [NON-ENGLISH], which was in a Jewish neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Usually yom tov time we can come together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Otherwise, because the family was so big, we rather visited each uncle or aunt separately.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not particularly.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Any, any Jewish holidays, we would be together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Mostly it was my mother's family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father's parents.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My, my grandma from my father's side I don't remember at all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My grandfather passed away when I was two years old.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "From my mother's side, the grandfather was still alive when the war started.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, our house was bombed, right away in the beginning of the war, on September 3rd.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we lost everything, and we moved to my grandfather and stayed there for a few weeks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother, Adam?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- he was, of course, six, six year-- he was six years younger than I was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I didn't spend too much time with him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was always busy with my friends.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, I don't-- from the childhood, I don't remember too much about our relationship.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the one, one thing I remember, one day he has a little car toy, was a-- was a glass-- was a convertible with a piece of glass as a, as a front window.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know what happened, but he sat on it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, of course, he cut himself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This one accident I remember vividly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You started to talk about your life after you were liberated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
